{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9e129c7231","title":"攻击青年团的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"62f4167326","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"9e129c7231"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5704f7fbe4","name":"邵恩吉"},{"id":"5fca8d9cc8","name":"叶仲乐"},{"id":"792e55d905","name":"刘玉林"},{"id":"82a3f7aa1a","name":"姜纯洪"},{"id":"c4cceb0823","name":"巩立龙"},{"id":"ccc3af54a9","name":"郭荣环"},{"id":"efce061973","name":"东北财经学院"},{"id":"f0868a5ad7","name":"李忠良"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"31b754b1e0","type":"title","text":"攻击青年团的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"21896b764e","type":"authors","text":"东北财经学院姜纯洪郭荣环叶仲乐邵恩吉李忠良刘玉林巩立龙","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"62f92fd6c7","type":"paragraph","text":"“青年团、少先队和国民党的三青团、童子军是一样的，没有什么区别，我参加团只是一种信仰，我入团是为了取得上级的信任，将来工作好作，入团就是往上爬，使自己取得名誉和地位。”(姜纯洪)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"261efc5b5a","type":"paragraph","text":"“团员只是开开会，没有什么意思，前二年我就不感兴趣了，一超令我就退团。”(郭荣环)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"6ef1be2de2","type":"paragraph","text":"“在财经学院这个环境中，不该提出入团申请书，这个团我永远也不去加入。”(刘蒙哥)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"68b332ac89","type":"paragraph","text":"“要求入党的团员是‘伪君子’，是‘宠儿’，是拍马溜须。”(叶仲乐)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"10f4d58c9a","type":"appellation","text":"“要整掉入党的拍马风，入团的不敢接近群众风。”(邵恩吉)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"d1d22b46ce","type":"paragraph","text":"“团员是狡猾的狐狸和多年有经验的老猴子。”(李忠良)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"1ad67dc54a","type":"paragraph","text":"“同学有三等五级之分。三等即党、团、群众；五级即党干部、党员、团干部、团员、群众。这种等级是以信任程度为标准。”(刘玉林)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"4d674c1436","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们班里有的团员也被压的喘不过气来，我在班里没有权利讲话，别人骂我不是人，我告诉石素琴，可是班内党团组织都不过问，我得不到温暖，甚至产生自杀念头。”(巩立龙)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"},{"id":"3426f22545","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《我院学生中的右派言论汇编》（中共东北财经学院委员会编，1957）","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231"}],"page":{"id":"77ddc2bc08","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9e129c7231","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}